u}_{\varphi}(x)=$ mult$(\widetilde{X},x). 
u_{\varphi}(x)$ for all $x\in \widetilde{X}$, where $ ar{
u}_{\varphi}(x)$ is the projective mass of a plurisubharmonic function $\varphi$ at $x$ and mult$(\widetilde{X},x)$ is the multiplicity of $\widetilde{X}$ at $x$ and $
u_{\varphi}(x)$ is Lelong number of $\varphi$ at $x$. Moreover, we show that the closure of the upper-level sets $\{z\in \widetilde{X}:
